d should be invocable\", exception);\n        } catch (InvocationTargetException exception) {\n            return exception;\n        }\n        throw new AssertionError(\"Expected plugin proxy invocation to fail\");\n    }\n\n    private static void withIsolatedMockito(IsolatedMockitoOperation operation) throws Exception {\n        Thread thread = Thread.currentThread();\n        ClassLoader originalLoader = thread.getContextClassLoader();\n        ClassLoader mockitoLoader = new IsolatedMockitoClassLoader(PluginLoaderTest.class.getClassLoader());\n        ClassLoader failingResourceLoader = new FailingMockitoExtensionResourceLoader(mockitoLoader);\n        try {\n            thread.setContextClassLoader(failingResourceLoader);\n            operation.run(mockitoLoader);\n        } finally {\n            thread.setContextClassLoader(originalLoader);\n        }\n    }\n\n    private static boolean hasUnsupportedFeatureError(Throwable throwable) {\n        Throwable current = throwable;\n        while (current != null) {\n            if (current instanceof Error error\n                    && NativeImageSupport.isUnsupportedFeatureError(error)) {\n                return true;\n            }\n            current = current.getCause();\n        }\n        return false;\n    }\n\n    private interface IsolatedMockitoOperation {\n        void run(ClassLoader mockitoLoader) throws Exception;\n    }\n\n    private static final class FailingMockitoExtensionResourceLoader extends ClassLoader {\n        private FailingMockitoExtensionResourceLoader(ClassLoader parent) {\n            super(parent);\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public Enumeration<URL> getResources(String name) throws IOException {\n            if (name.startsWith(\"mockito-extensions/\")) {\n                throw new IOException(\"Deliberate resource lookup failure for \" + name);\n            }\n            return super.getResources(name);\n        }\n    }\n\n    private static final class IsolatedMo